{"type":null,"faqId":47293,"title":"能否通过 USB 共享手机的移动网络？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:#333333;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">如果手机具备 USB 共享网络功能，您可以通过 USB 线将手机的移动网络共享给电脑。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">因为电脑操作系统的差异，在使用此功能前，可能需要在电脑中安装手机驱动程序或建立相应的网络连接，详情请参见电脑操作指导。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">通过 USB 数据线将手机连接到电脑，然后在“设置”界面，点击“更多”&gt;“网络共享与便携式热点”&gt; USB网络共享”，开启 USB网络共享功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=175712\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">电脑上网的流量耗费高于手机上网方式，建议在手机流量充足的情况下，开启该特性。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2860","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219192000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":62,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"USB,共享,移动网络","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}